snippet.title: RWBY: Amity Arena Pre-Registration Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description: RWBY: Amity Arena is finally available for pre-registration!  Go to the website to pre-register and to sign up for our newsletter!  rwbyaa.hangame.com  Have you ever wanted to see how your team of Huntsman and Huntresses would compete in the Vytal Festival Tournament? Now's your chance with RWBY: Amity Arena!
